Mike Robbins, to Google
San Francisco to talk

00:00:12.910 --> 00:00:16.470
about his latest book,
"Nothing Changes Until You Do."

00:00:16.470 --> 00:00:18.570
This is Mike's third book.

00:00:18.570 --> 00:00:21.990
He's also written two other
books that you may know,

00:00:21.990 --> 00:00:25.720
"Focus On the Good
Stuff" and "Be Yourself,

00:00:25.720 --> 00:00:28.520
Everyone Else is Already Taken."

